  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thrilling battles</h2>Wandering Desert Island features powerful bosses, dangerous dungeons, and monsters spawning in different island biomes.<br>You can match weapons and equipment to unlock powerful skills to slash, block, tumble and destroy these monsters to survive!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/1f2076bf159c1d56f2a45b3e9d0ee5d5.poster.avif?t=1719341682\" width=500 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/1f2076bf159c1d56f2a45b3e9d0ee5d5.webm?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/1f2076bf159c1d56f2a45b3e9d0ee5d5.mp4?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Classic sandbox survival gameplay</h2>Farming and fishing, cutting down trees and digging for mines, building huts, these are all indispensable.<br>However, you don't need pickaxes and axes to sabotage here, an iron sword is enough.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/4d41a8d420765f3cab2b08c7180d0ccb.poster.avif?t=1719341682\" width=500 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/4d41a8d420765f3cab2b08c7180d0ccb.webm?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/4d41a8d420765f3cab2b08c7180d0ccb.mp4?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock and grow technology</h2>Technology changes lives, and with these technologies, you can upgrade your home. Expanded lighting, rapid watering, resource regeneration...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/b118e289a9e8acd33cd6514aa2a76572.poster.avif?t=1719341682\" width=500 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/b118e289a9e8acd33cd6514aa2a76572.webm?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/b118e289a9e8acd33cd6514aa2a76572.mp4?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the island and visit NPCs</h2>Not all islands are deserted, and some are inhabited by residents! Deal with the residents and trade goods with them.<br>Each island has unique creatures and resources to explore.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/92a1b496bd84437d277e10f90a6d9967.poster.avif?t=1719341682\" width=500 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/92a1b496bd84437d277e10f90a6d9967.webm?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/92a1b496bd84437d277e10f90a6d9967.mp4?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thrilling battles</h2>Wandering Desert Island features powerful bosses, dangerous dungeons, and monsters spawning in different island biomes.<br>You can match weapons and equipment to unlock powerful skills to slash, block, tumble and destroy these monsters to survive!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/1f2076bf159c1d56f2a45b3e9d0ee5d5.poster.avif?t=1719341682\" width=500 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/1f2076bf159c1d56f2a45b3e9d0ee5d5.webm?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/1f2076bf159c1d56f2a45b3e9d0ee5d5.mp4?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Classic sandbox survival gameplay</h2>Farming and fishing, cutting down trees and digging for mines, building huts, these are all indispensable.<br>However, you don't need pickaxes and axes to sabotage here, an iron sword is enough.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/4d41a8d420765f3cab2b08c7180d0ccb.poster.avif?t=1719341682\" width=500 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/4d41a8d420765f3cab2b08c7180d0ccb.webm?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/4d41a8d420765f3cab2b08c7180d0ccb.mp4?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock and grow technology</h2>Technology changes lives, and with these technologies, you can upgrade your home. Expanded lighting, rapid watering, resource regeneration...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/b118e289a9e8acd33cd6514aa2a76572.poster.avif?t=1719341682\" width=500 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/b118e289a9e8acd33cd6514aa2a76572.webm?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/b118e289a9e8acd33cd6514aa2a76572.mp4?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the island and visit NPCs</h2>Not all islands are deserted, and some are inhabited by residents! Deal with the residents and trade goods with them.<br>Each island has unique creatures and resources to explore.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/92a1b496bd84437d277e10f90a6d9967.poster.avif?t=1719341682\" width=500 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/92a1b496bd84437d277e10f90a6d9967.webm?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/92a1b496bd84437d277e10f90a6d9967.mp4?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
